(CDPSEUDO
  [LAMBDA (PHOST CDSUFFIX FILEPKGFLG)                        (* ; "Edited 27-Apr-2026 22:54 by rmk")
                                                             (* ; "Edited 25-Apr-2026 23:53 by rmk")
